seen as a rival to Netflix. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-68530" src="https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-2.jpg?resize=740,359&amp;ssl=1" alt="Nigerian Filmmaker Michael Chineme Launches Micverse " width="740" height="359" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-2.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-2.jpg?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-2.jpg?resize=768%2C372&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" data-recalc-dims="1"> MicSquare: Social media section where users can connect and chat with friends and colleagues from all over the world. This features gives a feel that Michael wants to give Instagram a run for its money. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-68535" src="https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-6.jpg?resize=593,630&amp;ssl=1" alt="Nigerian Filmmaker Michael Chineme Launches Micverse " width="593" height="630" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-6.jpg?w=593&amp;ssl=1 593w, https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-6.jpg?resize=282%2C300&amp;ssl=1 282w" sizes="(max-width: 593px) 100vw, 593px" data-recalc-dims="1"> MicFundit: A crowdfunding section where users can raise funds for their creative projects. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-68534" src="https://i0.wp.com/techeconomy.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Nigerian-Filmmaker-Michael-Chineme-Launches-Micverse-5.jpg?resize=500,